d with streamwise velocity fluctuations and\nthere is a switch between high- and low-speed streaks at a particular height\nfor all stratified cases.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 5 Oct 2021 18:05:18 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 16 Nov 2021 10:37:12 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-11-17"}
