y role in determining the band structure of\nnanoparticles and the bandgap does not converge to the bulk limit for the\nparticle sizes investigated.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 5 Oct 2021 18:07:04 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-10-07"}
